de.mrapp.android.dialog.listener

Class AbstractListenerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.dialog.listener.AbstractListenerWrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OnClickListenerWrapper, OnItemClickListenerWrapper, OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper

    public abstract class AbstractListenerWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract base class for all wrappers, which implement a specific listener interface of a dialog's buttonType or list item, in order to delegate the method calls to an encapsulated listener of another type. Depending on the type of the buttonType or list item which causes the listener call, the appropriate dialog may be closed by the wrapper.
    Since:
    1.0.0
